p: \bI had an entire region to myself, and a legendary Pokemon.
\bI could have used the crystal to stop Her.
\bWe didn't need to have this problem.
\bBut you... you couldn't leave well enough alone, could you?
\bMy statues have been torn down... desecrated...
\bI went easy on you... but now I have nothing left to lose.
\bI am going to tear you to pieces! Bring it on!
\bI could have stopped Her, you know.
\bBut you ruined that. You forced my hand, and I got exposed.
\bI guess some advice wouldn't go amiss...
\bI learned about what was really going on behind the scenes while researching the First Augur's crystal.
\bIt seems to be a power source older than time itself.
\bI thought it contained nearly limitless energy... turns out, it actually is unlimited.
\bWith it, an entire universe could be created.
\bI don't remember much about Her... I don't know why. It's like there's a block in my memory.
\bBut She's stronger than you can imagine. You can't let Her get it.
\bHah... who am I kidding. You don't have a chance.
\bI'm going to enjoy my last few minutes on this planet before you ruin it.
